<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Ovi's Proofreading Portfolio</h1>
    <p>Hello! I’m Ovi, a dedicated proofreader with a sharp eye for detail and a passion for perfect writing. I help make your documents clear, error-free, and professional by fixing grammar, spelling, punctuation, and formatting issues. I’m reliable, fast, and committed to your satisfaction.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Sample 1: Academic Paragraph (Before & After)</h2>
    <p><strong>Before:</strong></p>
    <pre>The rapid advancement in technolgy has led to significant changes in our daily lifes. Many people has adapted new gadgets to improve their productivity. However, this also brought challenges such as privacy concerns.</pre>
    <p><strong>After:</strong></p>
    <pre>The rapid advancement in <span class="correction">technology</span> has led to significant changes in our daily <span class="correction">lives</span>. Many people <span class="correction">have</span> adapted new gadgets to improve their productivity. However, this also <span class="correction">brings</span> challenges such as privacy concerns.</pre>
    <p><em>Corrections:</em> Spelling errors, subject-verb agreement, verb tense consistency.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sample 2: Blog Post Excerpt (Before & After)</h2>
    <p><strong>Before:</strong></p>
    <pre>Travelling to new places are an exciting experience. It allow us to learn about different cultures and meet new people. But its important to plan ahead to avoid problems.</pre>
    <p><strong>After:</strong></p>
    <pre>Travelling to new places <span class="correction">is</span> an exciting experience. It <span class="correction">allows</span> us to learn about different cultures and meet new people. But <span class="correction">it’s</span> important to plan ahead to avoid problems.</pre>
    <p><em>Corrections:</em> Subject-verb agreement, verb agreement, contraction correction.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sample 3: Business Email (Before & After)</h2>
    <p><strong>Before:</strong></p>
    <pre>Dear Mr. Smith,  
Thank you for your email. I will looking into the issue and get back to you shortly. Please let me know if there is any other thing I can assist you with.

Best regards,  
Ovi</pre>
    <p><strong>After:</strong></p>
    <pre>Dear Mr. Smith,  
Thank you for your email. I will <span class="correction">look</span> into the issue and get back to you shortly. Please let me know if there is <span class="correction">anything else</span> I can assist you with.

Best regards,  
Ovi</pre>
    <p><em>Corrections:</em> Verb form, word choice.</p>
  </section>
